{"tid":1968730,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共：感謝熱狗帶領鬥黃成風 食肆不遵守6項規定或不獲薪金資助","createTime":"2020-04-12T01:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T03:05:13.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e9545f09c8cd13a64415375c1e6ca78aff0366af","tid":1968730,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T01:48:41.000Z","msg":"食環署︰如食肆不遵守6項規定或不獲資助<br />\n12.04.2020 08:58<br />\n<br />\n食環署署長劉利群在本台節目表示，自加強對食肆的規管後，食環署巡查過3萬2千次，發出1700多宗勸喻，及11宗檢控。她表示，現時勸喻階段已過，如發現有食肆違反任何一項規定，會即時作出檢控。<br />\n<br />\n劉利群又指，第二輪防疫抗疫基金計劃按照食肆的面積，作為計劃資助的基礎，每間持牌食肆可獲25萬至220萬元不等，食肆店主需要承諾不裁員，及用不少於8成的資助額支付員工薪酬，若有食肆不遵守加強規管措施，有機會不獲發資助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280276&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1280276%26csid%3D261_341&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1WwOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=21fe782d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280276&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"4c3cc839068f5d94c339c312d0930e03c3f1ac10","tid":1968730,"uid":37112,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T01:53:11.000Z","msg":"你不如話熱狗帶領鳩戴口罩成風<br />\n<br />\n黃衛兵鬥黃柒咗就入熱狗數👍🏻"},{"pid":"b7f86301d8f214f7b5ecb914ce92f36d8837d597","tid":1968730,"uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T01:58:36.000Z","msg":"熱狗講咗啲乜我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ebe76103f44a3a54520ec46ef70ab8d329aa23","tid":1968730,"uid":7603,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T02:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就黎呢排翻風轉涼都入熱狗數"},{"pid":"b06bc27bc4eace5283fead9be4dbe8d3600a854e","tid":1968730,"uid":110123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:03:52.000Z","msg":"樓豬一大清早就食熱狗，睇黎餓左幾日喎"},{"pid":"093f7d52ab1d4